msgstr "Transeúnte Molesto"

msgctxt "916"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "920"
msgid "Concerned Passerby"
msgstr "Transeúnte Preocupado"

msgctxt "924"
msgid "Talk_Quest"
msgstr "Talk_Quest"

msgctxt "84_Annoyed Passerby"
msgid "Wonder what this truck's doing here. Other than blocking the road, I mean."
msgstr "¿Qué rayos hace este camión aquí? Además de estar estorbando el tráfico, claro."

msgctxt "96_Concerned Passerby"
msgid "Do you think someone's moving?"
msgstr "¿Crees que alguien se está mudando?"

msgctxt "108_Annoyed Passerby"
msgid "Dunno. All I've seen is these beefy dudes carrying out boxes\\r\n"
"and boxes and boxes and boxes. Couldn't see what was in 'em, though."
msgstr "Ni idea. Lo único que vi fueron unos tipos bien fuertes sacando\\r\n"
"un montón de cajas, muchísimas cajas. Pero no se veía qué traían adentro."

msgctxt "120_Concerned Passerby"
msgid "I hope they finish soon, either way. This isn't how I\\r\n"
"envisioned our night out on the town..."
msgstr "A ver si terminan pronto, como sea. Esta no era la\\r\n"
"idea que tenía para nuestra noche de fiesta..."

